extends baseEmail
block content 
  p Hi #{firstName},
    p Forgot your password? Submit a patch request with your new password! and password confirm to: #{url}
    p We're all a big family here, so make sure to upload your user photo so we get to know you a bit better!
    p (website for this action not yet implemented.)
    table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
      tbody
        tr
          td(align='left')
            table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
              tbody
                tr
                  td
                    a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Reset your password
    p If you didn't forget the password please ignore this message!
    p - Asfand Yar.